The comedy world is in mourning following the death of Sean Lock from cancer at the age of 58. As well as being a team captain on the series 8 Out of 10 Cats, hosted by Jimmy Carr, Sean also also appeared on QI, The Last Leg, Have I Got News for You, and The Big Fat Quiz of the Year. But it was during his stand-up gigs that Sean really came into his own, winning a legion of fans. Here we remember the British comic with 11 of his finest gags... Additional reporting supplied by PA Media.